            "Original": "One of the most important properties of a temporary address is to make it difficult to link the address to different actions over time.",
            "Adjusted": "No change"
        },
        {
            "Original": "So, it is NOT RECOMMENDED for a client to renew temporary addresses, though DHCP provides for such a possibility (see Section 21.5).",
